                                        </h1>
                                        <p style="font-size: 20px; color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; opacity: 0.95;">
                                            Your journey into family history starts here
                                        </p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    
