                                            <h3 style="font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #333333;">
                                                Here's what you can do right now:
                                            </h3>
                                            <ol style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #666666;">
                                                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                                    <strong>Create your family tree</strong> - Start by adding yourself and your immediate family
                                                </li>
                                                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                                    <strong>Upload photos</strong> - Bring your family history to life with pictures
                                                </li>
                                                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                                    <strong>Share stories</strong> - Record memories and anecdotes for future generations
                                                </li>
                                                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                                    <strong>Invite family members</strong> - Collaborate to build a complete family tree
                                                </li>
                                            </ol>
                                        </div>
                                        
