                                        <h2 style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 20px 0; color: #333333;">
                                            üí° Quick Tips
                                        </h2>
                                        
                                        <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td valign="top" style="padding-right: 15px; font-size: 24px;">üì∏</td>
                                                <td>
                                                    <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #666666;">
